clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: Cabozantinib is indicated for the treatment of progressive metastatic medullary thyroid cancer L15123 It is also indicated for the treatment of advanced renal cell carcinoma and for hepatocellular carcinoma in patients previously treated with sorafenib L15128 L15133

contraindications.disease: Cabozantinib carries a warning of serious gastrointestinal fistulas and perforations and potentially fatal hemoptysis and gastrointestinal hemorrhage
contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Cabozantinib suppresses metastasis angiogenesis and oncognesis by inhibiting receptor tyrosine kinases
